Title: Astral Plane
Writer: Pendleton Ward (creator), Jesse Moynihan, Jillian Tamaki, Kent Osborne (story), Pendleton Ward (story), Jack Pendarvis (story), Adam Muto (story)
Actors: Jeremy Shada, John DiMaggio, Tom Kenny, Stephen Root
Plot: Finn and Jake go camping in the woods. When they go to sleep, Finn has an out-of-body experience and visits other creatures all around Ooo while he slowly ascends to space.
